The OP title is &quot;
Apple now rejecting apps with Pebble Smartwatch support&quot; 
Sorry but no Apple is not rejecting such apps... It just doesn&#x27;t want other product name mentioned.
And yes Apple is the gatekeeper of the Apple ecosystem... It is just the way it is.
I am not saying that what Apple is doing is right, but the OP statement is wrong
